thread.title: Leane

author: Leane
title: Leane
text: I was initially rather fearful about transferring funds internationally but I am so pleased that HiFX was recommended to me nearly 10 years ago. A few months back, my Australian bank suggested I use their own service so I asked for a Quote: on $A10,000. When they heard that I had received $NZ200 more than their Quote: through HiFX, they understood why I am a very satisfied client of HiFX.
